overview: JeetLe.in is a unique platform providing Web-based Contesting and Home Shopping opportunities each! The Web-based Contest comprises of the Reverse-Auctioning System which is the entire crux of JeetLe.in, where as JeetLe Deals will offer our customers discounted online-buying prospects for a better deal! The Reverse-Auctioning System is a unique and time-based bidding process that will allow you to buy/win a consumer product at the lowest price possible albeit the lowest and the unique price comes from you! It’s a strategic game plan that can be foolproof for your winning. Rest assured the JeetLe Deals will always be at your disposal for a discounted price of the same product! So it’s a win-win situation in both the cases!
